<blockquote>
  <p>2011 - International Foundation for Autonomous Agents and Multiagent Systems<br />
Author: Richard S. Sutton, Joseph Modayil, Michael Delp, Thomas Degris, Patrick M. Pilarski, Adam White<br />
Link: <a href="https://www.cs.swarthmore.edu/~meeden/DevelopmentalRobotics/horde1.pdf">原文链接</a></p>
